Tiberius, Your personal AI assistant 

(This is not a real "AI" but it fit the trend so why not)

Libraries Used
PortAudio
PyAudio - Audio Driver for Python
SpeechRecognition - SpeechRecognition which uses API's such as googleAPI 
Pyttsx3 -Text To Speech
datetime - allows for tiberius to return  the date and time


//CURRENT FUNCTIONALITY//
Tiberius will greet you as you begin to run the program
When asked for the "Date", he will tell you the current day of the week, what day of the month and which month it is

